passages.text:
I'm busy. Go bother someone else.
[[What are you doing back here?|What doing]]
[[Okay, bye!|Bye]]

links.name: What are you doing back here?|What doing
links.link: What are you doing back here?|What doing

passages.name: Start

passages.text:
None of your business. Who even are you? Do you always go around asking people you've never met stupid questions?
[[Yes.|Yes]]
[[You're acting suspicious.|Suspicious]]
passages.name: What doing

passages.text:
Well, quit it. People around here aren't going to like that, and unless you like having fish heads thrown at you, I would stop poking your nose in other people's lives.
[[Okay, bye.|Bye end]]
passages.name: Yes

passages.text:
How do you know? I've never seen you before, so you must be new. For all you know, digging holes behind churches is a perfectly normal pastime here.
[[Continue]]
passages.name: Suspicious

passages.text:
Are you trying to tell me my culture is weird just because it's different from yours? Get lost.
[[Okay, bye.|Bye end]]
passages.name: Continue
